  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT336-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ iravukkuṟi nayantāṉait tōḻi colli maṟuttatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">The confidante refusing, speaking to HIM who had been
          granted night trysts. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT336">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> ceṟuvārk kuvakai yākat teṟuvara</l>
          <l> vīṅkiṉam varupavō tēmpāy tuṟaiva</l>
          <l> ciṟunā voṇmaṇi viḷari yārppak</l>
          <l> kaṭumā neṭuntēr nēmi pōkiya</l>
          <l> viruṅkaḻi neytal pōla</l>
          <l> varuntiṉa ḷaḷiyaṇī pirintici ṉōḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l rend="indent">Being a pleasure to those who slander [her] ,</l>
          <l rend="indent8">so that it will scorch [her]</l>
          <l>will they come here in a group,</l>
          <l rend="indent6">o man from the ghat spread with honey?</l>
          <l rend="indent">Like blue waterlilies in the dark backwaters,</l>
          <l rend="indent">run over by the wheel of the long chariot with swift horses,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">while the small-tongued bright bells boom the Viḷari tune,</l>
          <l>she was troubled, the pitiable one you had separated from.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
